                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>The luxury to<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 apprehend </l>
                    <l>The luxury 'twould<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 be </l>
                    <l>To look at thee<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 a single time </l>
                    <l>An Epicure of Me </l>
                    <l>In whatsoever<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 Presence makes</l>
                    <l>Till for a further<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 food </l>
                    <l>I scarcely recollect<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 to starve<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>So first am I<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 supplied - </l>
                    <l>The luxury to<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 meditate </l>
                    <l>The luxury it was</l>
                    <l>To banquet on<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 thy Countenance </l>
                    <l>A Sumptuousness<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 bestows </l>
                    <l>On plainer Days, </l>
                    <l>Whose Table, far<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>As Certainty - can see -</l>
                    <l>Is laden with a<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 single Crumb -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>The Consciousness -<app type="division"><lem><lb/></lem></app>
 of Thee - </l>
                </lg>

